stickerText: *trying to pop a “pimple”
“that hurt a lot more than normal…”
*2 days go by*
“OUCH!”
“oh my god…”
“MOM! remember that pimple i had the other day..? look at it now. it hurts SO bad.”
“let me see… oh that doesn’t look good. keep it clean ok?”
“ok i’ll try… ive never had a pimple hurt so much”
*the next few days…*
*waking up and deciding to take the bandage off*
“hey liv… will you go to the ER with me..?”
“yeah girly pop get ready, be there in 5”
*on our way to the ER*
“what can we help you with today?”
“i have this pimple and it hurts WAY to bad and it won’t go away”
“yikes… honey that’s not a pimple. why don’t you lay back and close your eyes…”
